data.title: Makefile.am
data.text:
Makefile.am [plain text]

AUTOMAKE_OPTIONS = gnu dist-zip 1.4-p5 SUBDIRS = admin bin etc include iodbc iodbcinst iodbcadm drvproxy samples EXTRA_DIST = \ IAFA-PACKAGE \ LICENSE LICENSE.LGPL LICENSE.BSD \ README.MACOSX \ mac/Makefile \ mac/README.MYODBC \ mac/myodbc.configure.diff \ mac/framework-include.sh \ mac/iODBC/English.lproj/InfoPlist.strings \ mac/iODBC/iODBC.pbproj/project.pbxproj \ mac/iODBCinst/English.lproj/InfoPlist.strings \ mac/iODBCinst/iODBCinst.pbproj/project.pbxproj \ mac/iODBCtest/iODBCtest.pbproj/project.pbxproj \ mac/iodbc.exp \ mac/iodbcinst.exp \ debian/changelog \ debian/control \ debian/copyright \ debian/iodbc.files \ debian/iodbc.undocumented \ debian/libiodbc2-dev.examples \ debian/libiodbc2-dev.files \ debian/libiodbc2.docs \ debian/libiodbc2.examples \ debian/libiodbc2.files \ debian/libiodbc2.undocumented \ debian/rules MAINTAINERCLEANFILES = Makefile.in aclocal.m4 configure if MAINTAINER_MODE linux-rpm: $(MAKE) dist cp libiodbc-$(VERSION).tar.gz /usr/src/redhat/SOURCES rpm -ba admin/libiodbc.spec binary-tar: -mkdir @build@ $(MAKE) install prefix=`pwd`/@build@ tar cvf @build@.tar @build@ gzip -9vf @build@.tar rm -rf @build@ snapshot: $(MAKE) dist distdir=$(PACKAGE)-`date +"%Y%m%d"` release: $(MAKE) distcheck endif
